JAVASCRIPT:
=========
it is a client side scripting language and programming language which provide functionality to the web pages.

it is used to create dynamic and interactive web pages. 
it is a high level programming language which is easy to learn and use.
it is a versatile language which can be used for both front end and back end development. 

it is a popular language which is widely used in web development. 
it is a powerful language which can be used to create complex web applications. 
it is a language which is supported by all modern web browsers. it is a language which is constantly evolving and improving.

==========================================================================================================================

REACT:
=====

===========================================================================================|
|        SPA                                           MPA(TRADITION APPLICATION)          |
===========================================================================================|
                                                        
- IT LOADS SINGLE HTML PAGE                     MULTIPLE HTML FILE                         |
  UPDATES THE PAGE DYNOMICALLY                  
                                                                                           |
- IT HAVING INITIAL LOAD                        EVERY HTML FILE HAVE LOAD TIME             |

- THERE IS NO RELOAD                            IT WILL TAKE RELOAD ENTIRE applications    |

- It updates fast                               It updates slow                            |

-DOM manipulation is very easy                DOM manipulation is very expensive           |

- V-DOM :                                        REAL DOM :                                |

- REACT,angular,                              JAVASCRIPT,php,                              |

===========================================================================================|
================================================================================================================================

LIBRARY — you call it. You import it, use what you need, and stay in charge of the flow. It's a tool you pick up and put down.

(REACT is a Library)


FRAMEWORK — it calls you. You write code inside its structure, following its rules and conventions. It provides the skeleton; you fill in the flesh.

(ANGULAR,VEW, TAILWIND CSS is a Framework)
(REACT is not a Framework)

==================================================================================================================================

REACT JS : 
=========

- IT IS AN LIBRARY OF JAVASCRIPT used TO create interactive UI
- it is used to create SPA
- IT WAS DEVELOPED BY "JORDAN WALKE",WHO WAS WORKING IN THE FACEBOOK(META)
- IN THE PROTOTYPE VERSION THA NAME OF REACT.JS WAS FAX.JS
 
- IN 2011 THEY DEVELOPED REACT JS FOR THERE INTERNAL USED
- IN 2012 THEY DEPLOYED IT ON FACEBOOK NEW FEED AND THEN INSTAGRAM
- IN 2013 THEY MADE IT OPEN SOURCE SO THAT ANY ONE CAN USE

- IT IS USE VIRTUAL DOM
- IT IS COMPONENT BASED ARCHITECTURE(REUSE THE FILE LIKE AS AN COMPONENT)
- IT IS ONE- WAY DATA-BINDING IS PRESENT 
- UNI-DIRECTIONAL 
- IT IS DECLARATIVE











